<function>

access:   protected

name: _bc_exgcd

param: string, $x

param: string, $y

return: array

</function>

Finds the extended greatest-common-denominator of two values
using bcmath functions.

* Parameters:

 * string //$x//: First value.

 * string //$y//: Second value.

* Returns array: Extended GCD of $x and $y.